            generateFromText: "# INSTRUCTION: HIGH-QUALITY IMAGE GENERATION\n\n## 1. USER PROMPT:\n'{{prompt}}'\n\n## 2. EXECUTION:\n- Create a new, original image based on the user's prompt.\n- Prioritize creativity, detail, and professional composition.\n- Pay close attention to lighting, mood, and texture to create a visually striking result.\n- The final image must be high-resolution (2K). If the user requests a specific style (e.g., hyperrealistic, anime, watercolor), adhere to it strictly. If no style is mentioned, aim for photorealism.",
